Package: BIODICAPT-OED-V0
Title: OED workflow for BIODICAPT
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Loïc",
        family = "Lehnhoff",
        role = c("cre", "auth", "cph"),
        email = "loic.lehnhoff@mnhn.fr"
        )
    )
Description: Pipeline for Optimal Experimental Design (OED) applied to 
BIODICAPT. The pipeline includes the loading and pre-processing of the 
datasets, the setup and comparison of distribution models (SDM/SSDM/jSDM)
and the determination of the OED under custom cost functions.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8

